Đồ án Máy học¶

Phan Thành Đăng, Nguyễn Phạm Quốc Huy, Phùng Việt Lâm¶

Phát hiện sửa đổi phá hoại trên Wikipedia tiếng Việt¶

1. Giới thiệu¶

Wikipedia l bch khoa ton th m trc tuyn a ngn ng c sng lp v duy tr bi mt cng ng bin tp vin tnh nguyn v chy trn nn tng wiki. Hin nay, Wikipedia c n 309 phin bn ngn ng khc nhau trn ton cu [1]. Trong , Wikipedia ting Vit thuc nhm phin bn ngn ng c tr lng bi vit nhiu nht th gii, vi 1.267.713 bi vit, 19.298.695 trang ni b, 815.944 thnh vin c ti khon v 2.496 thnh vin tch cc (c hot ng trong 30 ngy gn nht) [2].

Wikipedia c tnh m, ngha l phn ln ni dung ca n u c cng ng ng gp v tch ly qua thi gian. Nhng ng gp ca cng ng c quy v khi nim sa i, c th l hnh vi to mt bi vit mi, chnh li ni dung mt on vn, sa li chnh t hay thm mt lin kt, v.v. Phn ln cc sa i u c v l hp l v c ch cho vic xy dng mt bch khoa ton th, c gi l sa i thin [3]. Nhng mt phn trong cc sa i c xem l sa i ph hoi.

"Ph hoi l bt k hnh ng thm, xa hoc sa i ni dung c c tnh thc hin nhm lm hi tnh ton vn ca Wikipedia" [4]. c th l hnh vi c ty trng ni dung bi vit, thm t ng tc tu, hay phc tp hn l chn cc thng tin gi, sai s tht, ba t mt cch tinh vi, iu chnh vn phong theo hng c li cho mt phe tuyn truyn chnh tr, v.v. Ph hoi khng ch gii hn ti Wikipedia, m cn l mt hnh vi c trng ca nhng nn tng m nh Facebook, WikiMapia hay OpenStreetMaps [5].

Mi ngy, Wikipedia ting Vit n nhn khong 3200 sa i, bao gm sa i ca thnh vin c ti khon ( ng nhp) v cha c ti khon (dng IP), theo s liu lch s sa i t ngy 01/04/2021 n ngy 30/06/2021 [6]. Mt c tnh cho thy khong 7% tng sa i ca Wikipedia c xem l ph hoi [7]. Do , Wikipedia ting Vit c th c khong 200300 sa i ph hoi mi ngy.

Hin nhin, mi hnh vi mang tnh ph hoi u s khng c cho n bt c ni u. V mt truyn thng, cc sa i trn Wikipedia s c mt nhm cc thnh vin tnh nguyn kim tra, nh gi v hy b nu nh sa i l ph hoi. Mt h thng kim tra bi con ngi s gp phi tr ngi ln nu nh khng ngi tham gia mt cng vic khng lng thng, d cho l kh chnh xc. Vn thiu nhn lc tnh nguyn lun l mt bi ton kh i vi d n Wikipedia ting Vit [8]. Do , vic trin khai mt h thng kim tra, nh gi v pht hin sa i ph hoi trn c s cc m hnh my hc l rt cn thit.

Ti Wikipedia ting Anh, c nhng cng c t ng hoc bn t ng nhm h tr pht hin cc sa i ph hoi. Ni bt nht c th k n l ClueBot NG, STiki v Snuggle; s dng cc lut heuristic v thut ton my hc nhm d ra ph hoi [5]. Trong , ClueBot NG l cng c chng ph hoi kinh in ca Wikipedia ting Anh [5], s dng cc thut ton my hc ni ting nh phn lp Bayes v mng neuron nhn to; gip kim tra, nh gi v hy b cc sa i ph hoi mt cch t ng [9]. Bn cnh , Qu Wikimedia (t chc qun l h thng cc wiki bao gm Wikipedia) cng c mt d n "my hc nh mt dch v" (machine learning as a service) l ORES, vi nhiu m hnh d bo cho nhiu hot ng khc nhau, nh m hnh tnh xc sut kh nng mt sa i c xem l ph hoi [10]. Wikipedia ting Vit c th trin khai nhng cng c tng t nh ca Wikipedia ting Anh hay ORES nhm gii quyt bi ton x l ph hoi trong tnh trng thiu nhn lc.

Hnh 1. ORES gip phn loi sa i ph hoi v thin

1.1 Mục tiêu¶

n "Pht hin sa i ph hoi trn Wikipedia ting Vit" c mc tiu l xy dng c cc m hnh da trn cc thut ton my hc c ging dy, c chnh xc cao nhm gii quyt bi ton pht hin cc sa i ph hoi trn Wikipedia ting Vit. ng thi, rt ra c quy trnh c bn xy dng cc m hnh phn lp.

1.2 Giới hạn¶

  • D liu (dataset) c ly t Wikipedia ting Vit.
  • Thut ton my hc c s dng xy dng cc m hnh gm c: SVM, Hi quy logistic v k-Means, c th s dng thm mt s thut ton khc i snh.

1.3 Định dạng¶

Ti liu ny c trnh by theo hng va gii thch tng bc trong quy trnh thc hin n, ng thi c gi tr bo co nh mt bi bo khoa hc.

2. Chuẩn bị dữ liệu¶

Chun b d liu (Data Preparation) l qu trnh x l d liu th thnh d liu thch hp cho vic xy dng m hnh my hc [11]. Qu trnh chun b d liu c th gm cc bc sau [12] [13]:

  1. Thu thp d liu
  2. Thm d d liu
  3. S ch d liu
  4. Trch chn c trng
  5. Gim chiu d liu

2.1 Thu thập dữ liệu¶

Thu thp d liu (Data Collection) l qu trnh tm kim v trch nht nhng thng tin lin quan n vn nghin cu, to ra d liu th (raw data) [13].

Mt b d liu (dataset) c t chc theo hai thnh phn l cc mu d liu (samples) v cc c trng ca d liu (features) [14], c biu din tng ng di dng cc hng v ct ca mt bng d liu.

B d liu ca n ny c thu thp bng cch s dng th vin revscoring (Revision Scoring), mt phn mm dng xy dng ORES.

2.1.1 Cơ sở thu thập dữ liệu¶

Trc khi bt tay vo vic thu thp d liu bng revscoring, cn phi bit c l s thu thp nhng d liu no. n c mc tiu l pht hin nhng sa i ph hoi, ngha l cn thu thp d liu nhng c trng xoay quanh cc sa i.

Mt sa i Wikipedia c th chia lm 2 loi chnh: Sa i to trang v Sa i sa trang. Mt s thng tin khi qut:

  • Sa i to trang l sa i to ra mt trang (Page) mi, ng thi cng to ra bn sa i (Revision) u tin ca trang . V d mt bn sa i c to ra bi sa i to trang: 65193673.

  • Sa i sa trang l sa i c thc hin trn mt trang c to trc , thay i ni dung ca trang v to ra bn sa i mi ca trang. V d mt bn sa i c to ra bi sa i sa trang: 65193680.

  • S thay i ni dung (thm, xa, sa) gia 2 bn sa i bt k ca cng 1 trang c gi l s khc bit (Diff). V d s khc bit gia bn sa i 65193673 v 65193680 ca trang "Nguyn Vn Thi (nh bo tn)": Diff(65193673~65193680).

  • Mt trang c th c mt hay nhiu bn sa i, s lng bn sa i ca trang bng vi s lng lt sa i ca trang . Mi mt lt sa i to ra 1 bn sa i mi ca trang.

  • Sa i c thc hin bi ngi dng (User). Ngi dng c 2 nhm: ng k ti khon v Cha ng k ti khon. Nhm ngi dng cha ng k ti khon khi thc hin sa i s c lu vt a ch IP.

Nh vy, vic thu thp d liu cc sa i chnh l thu thp d liu nhng c trng xoay quanh i tng bn sa i (Revision), v mi mt lt sa i u to ra 1 bn sa i mi. Thng tin nhng c trng ca bn sa i c th n t cc i tng c lin quan nh trang (Page), s khc bit (Diff), ngi dng (User) hay chnh bn sa i (Revision). Mi mt bn sa i u c mt m nh danh (Revision ID).

Th vin revscoring h tr thu thp cc thng tin xoay quanh cc bn sa i.

2.1.2 Thực hiện thu thập dữ liệu¶

u tin, cn thu thp mt danh sch cc bn sa i, biu din di dng m nh danh. Chn c mu l 20000 bn sa i, c ly ngu nhin trong s cc bn sa i c to ra trong thi gian 1 nm (01/08/2020 - 01/08/2021), khng c ly cc bn sa i to bi ti khon bot(*).

thc hin vic ny, cn dng Quarry, mt cng c cho php to cc truy vn SQL trc tip n bn sao c s d liu ca Wikipedia [16]. Truy vn 57765 trn Quarry c thc hin, vi m SQL nh sau:

SELECT rev_id
FROM revision
    JOIN actor on rev_actor = actor_id
WHERE rev_timestamp BETWEEN "20200801" AND "20210801"
    AND (actor_user NOT IN (SELECT ug_user
                            FROM user_groups
                            WHERE ug_group = "bot")
         OR actor_user IS NULL)
    AND actor_name NOT REGEXP "([Bb]ot|AWB)$"
ORDER BY RAND() 
LIMIT 20000;

Ti kt qu truy vn (danh mc Revision ID) v di dng tp CSV: revids.csv (th mc data).

(*): Ti khon bot l nhng ti khon dng cc cng c t ng thc hin cc sa i n gin, lp i lp li theo quy lut cho trc [15].

import sys, traceback
import mwreverts.api
import mwapi

# We'll use the mwreverts API check. In order to do that, we need an API session
session = mwapi.Session("https://vi.wikipedia.org", user_agent="Extract Revert Information")

# For each revision, find out if it was "reverted" and label it so.
rev_reverteds = []
for rev_id in revids[:20]:  # NOTE: Limiting to the first 20!!!!
    try:
        _, reverted, reverted_to = mwreverts.api.check(
            session, rev_id, radius=5,  # most reverts within 5 edits
            window=48*60*60,  # 2 days
            rvprop={'user', 'ids'})  # Some properties we'll make use of
    except (RuntimeError, KeyError) as e:
        sys.stderr.write(str(e))
        continue
    
    if reverted is not None:
        reverted_doc = [r for r in reverted.reverteds
                        if r['revid'] == rev_id][0]

        if 'user' not in reverted_doc or 'user' not in reverted.reverting:
            continue

        # self-reverts
        self_revert = \
            reverted_doc['user'] == reverted.reverting['user']
        
        # revisions that are reverted back to by others
        reverted_back_to = \
            reverted_to is not None and \
            'user' in reverted_to.reverting and \
            reverted_doc['user'] != \
            reverted_to.reverting['user']
        
        # If we are reverted, not by self or reverted back to by someone else, 
        # then, let's assume it was damaging.
        damaging_reverted = not (self_revert or reverted_back_to)
    else:
        damaging_reverted = False
    
    rev_reverteds.append([rev_id, "1" if damaging_reverted else "0"])
    sys.stderr.write("r" if damaging_reverted else ".")

import requests, json

def extract_features(rev_id):
    revision = requests.get('https://ores.wikimedia.org/v3/scores/viwiki/{0}/reverted?features'.format(rev_id)).json()
    return list(revision['viwiki']['scores'][str(rev_id)]['reverted']['features'].values())

raw_revs = []
for row in rev_reverteds.values[:20]: # NOTE: 20 phn t u ca rev_reverteds.csv
    try:
        rev_id = row[0]
        reverted = row[1]
        features = extract_features(rev_id) # D liu 90 c trng

        rev = [rev_id] + features + [reverted]
        raw_revs.append(rev)
        sys.stderr.write('.')
    except (RuntimeError, KeyError) as e:
        sys.stderr.write(str(rev_id))
        continue

def feature_names():
    revision = requests.get('https://ores.wikimedia.org/v3/scores/viwiki/1/reverted?features').json()
    return list(revision['viwiki']['scores']['1']['reverted']['features'].keys())

# Lu d liu ca bin raw_revs vo tp raw_revs.csv
pd.DataFrame(raw_revs, columns = ['rev_id'] + feature_names() + ['reverted']).to_csv('data/raw_revs.csv', index=False)

2.3 Sơ chế dữ liệu¶

S ch d liu (Data Wrangling) l qu trnh chuyn i d liu th thnh dng d liu thch hp cho cc cng vic x l sau ny, gip ci thin chnh xc ca m hnh my hc [20]. S ch d liu bao gm cc cng vic ca Lm sch d liu (Data Cleaning) v Chuyn i d liu (Data Transformation).

Mt s cng vic trong giai on S ch d liu:

  1. Xa cc ct ch cha 1 gi tr
  2. Xa cc hng trng lp
  3. Xa cc im ngoi lai (outlier)
  4. Chuyn i quy m d liu (Scaling Transformation)
  5. Chuyn i phn phi d liu (Distribution Transformation)
  6. M ha nhn bin nh tnh (Label Encoding)

Qu trnh s ch d liu tp raw_revs.csv c mt s im cn lu :

  • Cng vic chuyn i quy m v phn phi d liu ch p dng cho cc bin nh lng lin tc.
  • Phng php chuyn i quy m d liu l Chun ha mnh (Robust Standardization), trin khai thng qua lp RobustScaler ca sklearn. Vic la chn phng php ny l do Chun ha mnh thch hp x l d liu nhiu outlier, khng nh Chun ha (Standardization) v Bnh thng ha (Normalization) d nhy cm vi cc outlier [21] [22] [23].
  • Phng php chuyn i phn phi d liu l Chuyn i phn v chun (Normal Quantile Transform), trin khai thng qua lp QuantileTransformer ca sklearn. Vic la chn phng php ny cng v l do thch hp x l d liu nhiu outlier. Chuyn i phn v chun gip chuyn i phn phi ban u thnh dng phn phi chun [24].
  • M ha nhn bin nh tnh l vic chuyn i gi tr True, False hin ti ca cc bin nh tnh thnh dng s tng ng l 1, 0; thng qua lp OrdinalEncoder ca sklearn, thch hp cho vic trin khai cc thut ton my hc.
  • Khng tin hnh cng vic xa cc im ngoi lai (outlier) v s lng outlier qu nhiu, do nu xa c th gy nh hng n cht lng kt qu sau ny [25]. C th cn i snh gia vic xa v khng xa outlier khi kim nh m hnh.

2.4 Trích chọn đặc trưng¶

Trch chn c trng (Feature Selection) l qu trnh chn ra nhng c trng dng trong hun luyn m hnh. Li ch ca vic ny l gip gim khi lng d liu khng cn thit, gim thi gian hun luyn v tng cng tng qut ha bng cch gim s qu khp (overfitting) [26].

Phng php trch chn c trng c s dng trong n l Thng tin tng h (Mutual Information), trin khai thng qua hm mutual_info_classif ca sklearn. Nguyn nhn la chn l do phng php ny p dng tt i vi c bin u vo nh lng v nh tnh [27]. S c trng c trch trn tng s c trng ca b d liu l 70, nguyn nhn la chn con s 70 c gii thch Ph lc 3.

Di y l chng trnh s ch d liu v trch chn c trng i vi tp raw_revs.csv, kt qu c lu vo tp revs.csv.

In [15]:
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from sklearn.pipeline import Pipeline
from sklearn.preprocessing import RobustScaler, QuantileTransformer, OrdinalEncoder
from sklearn.compose import ColumnTransformer
from sklearn.feature_selection import SelectKBest, mutual_info_classif

# Ly d liu th
df = pd.read_csv('data/raw_revs.csv')

# Xa ct u tin 'rev_id' v khng cn thit
del df['rev_id']

# Xa cc ct ch cha 1 gi tr (c 3 ct)
df.drop(columns=df.columns[df.nunique()==1], inplace=True)

# Xa cc hng trng lp (c 10 hng)
df.drop_duplicates(inplace=True)

# Chuyn i cc bin nh lng v nh tnh
X, y = df.iloc[:, :-1], df.iloc[:, -1]

numerical_features = X.select_dtypes(include=np.number).columns.tolist()
numerical_transformer = Pipeline(steps=[
    ('scaler', RobustScaler(with_centering=False, with_scaling=True)),
    ('quantile', QuantileTransformer(n_quantiles=100, output_distribution='normal'))])

categorical_features = X.select_dtypes(bool).columns.tolist()
categorical_transformer = OrdinalEncoder()

preprocessor = ColumnTransformer(
    transformers=[
        ('num', numerical_transformer, numerical_features),
        ('cat', categorical_transformer, categorical_features)])

X_trans = pd.DataFrame(preprocessor.fit_transform(X),
                      columns = numerical_features + categorical_features)

# Trch chn c trng
X_trans = X_trans.loc[:, SelectKBest(score_func=lambda X, y: mutual_info_classif(X, y, random_state=0), k=70)
                      .fit(X_trans, y).get_support()]

# Lu kt qu s ch v trch chn vo bin result
result = X_trans
result['reverted'] = y.values

# Lu result vo revs.csv
result.to_csv('data/revs.csv', index=False)

3. Xây dựng và đánh giá mô hình¶

n s xy dng cc m hnh my hc gip d on mt sa i Wikipedia l ph hoi hay khng ph hoi, s dng 3 thut ton c ging dy: SVM, Hi quy logistic v k-Means. Mt s thut ton khc cng c s dng i snh: Gradient Boosting, Random Forest v k-NN (k lng ging gn nht).

Thit lp hm tng qut build_and_eval_model(clf) xy dng v nh gi m hnh nhm trin khai cho nhiu thut ton cp. Cc bc ca hm:

  1. Ly d liu revs.csv
  2. Tch d liu thnh bin input X v output y
    • X gm cc bin u vo nh lng v nh tnh (70 c trng)
    • y l bin phn lp nh phn
  3. Phn chia d liu thnh 2 tp: Training Set (70%) v Test Set (30%). Bo tn t l phn lp (stratify=y).
  4. Khi to m hnh, nhn thut ton phn lp thng qua tham s clf (classifier) ca hm.
  5. nh gi m hnh bng Kim chng cho (Cross Validation) trn Training Set
    • nh gi 4 h s: Accuracy ( chnh xc tng qut), Precision ( chnh xc), Recall ( nhy), F1.
    • Cross Validation c 5 fold, 3 ln lp li, bo tn t l phn lp (stratified). Trin khai thng qua lp RepeatedStratifiedKFold ca sklearn.
    • Kim chng cho m hnh trn Training Set, kt qu nh gi c lu vo tp <clf>_cv_scores.csv
  6. Hun luyn m hnh v dng m hnh d on trn Test Set
  7. nh gi kt qu d on ca m hnh trn Test Set
    • nh gi 4 h s: Accuracy ( chnh xc tng qut), Precision ( chnh xc), Recall ( nhy), F1.
    • Lu kt qu nh gi vo tp <clf>_final_scores.csv
  8. Trc quan ha kt qu nh gi
    • V biu hp cho 4 h s nh gi t kt qu kim chng cho Training Set.
    • V Confusion Matrix cho kt qu d on ca m hnh trn Test Set.
Hnh 2. K thut Kim chng cho (Cross Validation) [28]
In [3]:
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split, cross_validate, RepeatedStratifiedKFold
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, precision_score, recall_score, f1_score
from sklearn.metrics import plot_confusion_matrix

def build_and_eval_model(clf):
    # ly d liu
    df = pd.read_csv('data/revs.csv')

    # Tch d liu thnh bin input X v output y
    X, y = df.iloc[:, :-1], df.iloc[:, -1]

    # Phn chia d liu, bo tn t l phn lp (stratify=y).
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.3, stratify=y, random_state=0)

    # Khi to m hnh
    model = clf

    # nh gi m hnh bng Kim chng cho trn Training Set
    scoring = ['accuracy', 'precision', 'recall', 'f1']
    cv = RepeatedStratifiedKFold(n_splits=5, n_repeats=3, random_state=0)
    scores = cross_validate(model, X_train, y_train, scoring=scoring, cv=cv, n_jobs=-1, error_score='raise')
    cv_scores = pd.DataFrame(scores).iloc[:, 2:]
    print('A. Cross Validation on Training Set')
    print(cv_scores.describe())

    # Hun luyn m hnh
    model.fit(X_train, y_train)

    # Dng m hnh d on trn Test Set
    y_pred = model.predict(X_test)

    # nh gi kt qu d on ca m hnh trn Test Set
    final_scores = pd.DataFrame({'accuracy': [accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred)],
                                 'precision': [precision_score(y_test, y_pred)],
                                 'recall': [recall_score(y_test, y_pred)],
                                 'f1': [f1_score(y_test, y_pred)]})
    print('B. Final Validation on Test Set')
    print(final_scores.to_string(index=False))

    # Trc quan ha kt qu nh gi
    fig, axs = plt.subplots(1,2, figsize=(12,4))
    sns.boxplot(data=cv_scores, orient="h", palette="Set2", ax=axs[0])
    plot_confusion_matrix(model, X_test, y_test, cmap=plt.cm.Blues, ax=axs[1])
    plt.show()

    # Lu kt qu nh gi
    cv_scores.to_csv('data/{}_cv_scores.csv'.format(clf.__class__.__name__), index=False)
    final_scores.to_csv('data/{}_final_scores.csv'.format(clf.__class__.__name__), index=False)

import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split, cross_validate, RepeatedStratifiedKFold
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, precision_score, recall_score, f1_score
from sklearn.metrics import plot_confusion_matrix, confusion_matrix
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans

def build_and_eval_model(clf):
    # ly d liu
    df = pd.read_csv('data/revs.csv')

    # Tch d liu thnh bin input X v output y
    X, y = df.iloc[:, :-1], df.iloc[:, -1]

    # Phn chia d liu, bo tn t l phn lp (stratify=y).
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.3, stratify=y, random_state=0)

    # Khi to m hnh
    model = clf

    # nh gi m hnh bng Kim chng cho trn Training Set
    scoring = ['accuracy', 'precision', 'recall', 'f1']
    cv = RepeatedStratifiedKFold(n_splits=5, n_repeats=3, random_state=0)
    scores = cross_validate(model, X_train, y_train, scoring=scoring, cv=cv, n_jobs=-1, error_score='raise')
    cv_scores = pd.DataFrame(scores).iloc[:, 2:]
    print('A. Cross Validation on Training Set')
    print(cv_scores.describe())

    # Hun luyn m hnh
    model.fit(X_train, y_train)

    # Dng m hnh d on trn Test Set
    y_pred = model.predict(X_test)

    # nh gi kt qu d on ca m hnh trn Test Set
    final_scores = pd.DataFrame({'accuracy': [accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred)],
                                 'precision': [precision_score(y_test, y_pred)],
                                 'recall': [recall_score(y_test, y_pred)],
                                 'f1': [f1_score(y_test, y_pred)]})
    print('B. Final Validation on Test Set')
    print(final_scores.to_string(index=False))

    # Trc quan ha kt qu nh gi
    fig, axs = plt.subplots(1,2, figsize=(12,4))
    sns.boxplot(data=cv_scores, orient="h", palette="Set2", ax=axs[0])
    # plot_confusion_matrix(model, X_test, y_test, cmap=plt.cm.Blues, ax=axs[1])
    cm = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred)
    plt.imshow(cm, interpolation='none', cmap='Blues')
    for (i, j), z in np.ndenumerate(cm):
        plt.text(j, i, z, ha='center', va='center')
    plt.xlabel("Cluster label")
    plt.ylabel("True label")
    plt.show()

    # Lu kt qu nh gi
    cv_scores.to_csv('data/{}_cv_scores.csv'.format(clf.__class__.__name__), index=False)
    final_scores.to_csv('data/{}_final_scores.csv'.format(clf.__class__.__name__), index=False)

4. Kết luận¶

4.1 Đánh giá giữa các mô hình¶

Di y l biu hp so snh cc h s nh gi gia cc m hnh my hc c xy dng gii quyt bi ton ban u. Gm c 4 biu cho 4 h s: Accuracy ( chnh xc tng qut), Precision ( chnh xc), Recall ( nhy), F1. Chia lm 2 nhm biu : Nhm 1 gm tt c cc thut ton phn lp, Nhm 2 tng t nhng loi k-Means.

In [7]:
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

clf_names = ['SVC', 'LogisticRegression', 'KMeans', 'GradientBoostingClassifier',
            'RandomForestClassifier', 'KNeighborsClassifier']
score_names = ['test_accuracy', 'test_precision', 'test_recall', 'test_f1']

def build_plots(title):
    model_cv_scores = {clf_name: pd.read_csv('data/{}_cv_scores.csv'.format(clf_name)) for clf_name in clf_names}

    fig, axs = plt.subplots(2,2, figsize=(12,6))

    for score_name, ax in zip(score_names, axs.flat):
        score_data = pd.DataFrame({clf_name: model_cv_scores[clf_name][score_name] for clf_name in clf_names})
        sns.boxplot(data=score_data, orient="h", palette="Set2", ax=ax)
        ax.set_title(score_name)
    
    fig.suptitle(title)
    plt.tight_layout()

# Nhm 1: V biu  cho tt c clf
build_plots('ALL CLASSIFIERS')

# Nhm 2: V biu  cho tt c clf, tr k-Means
clf_names.remove('KMeans')
build_plots('CLASSIFIERS WITHOUT k-MEANS')

Nhn vo 4 biu Nhm 1, cho thy thut ton k-Means c cc gi tr h s chnh lch, bt thng so vi cc thut ton phn lp in hnh (k-Means bn cht l thut ton phn cm). Accuracy ca k-Means thp ng k so vi cc thut ton khc nn khng ph hp p dng cho bi ton ny.

Nhn vo 4 biu Nhm 2, ta c mt s kt lun:

Accuracy ( chnh xc tng qut) cao (gn bng 1) tt c m hnh. Tuy nhin, Accuracy c o lng c 2 lp "Sa i ph hoi" v "Sa i khng ph hoi", iu ny dn n h s Accuracy t ra khng ph hp nh gi cc m hnh ca bi ton ny. Do mc tiu bi ton l pht hin "Sa i ph hoi", do vic ny quan trng hn l pht hin "Sa i khng ph hoi". Vic pht hin chnh xc nhiu "Sa i khng ph hoi" khng c ngha vi mc tiu ra. Cn s dng nhng h s nh Precision, Recall o lng chuyn bit trn lp "Sa i ph hoi" [29]. Accuracy ch ph hp dng cho nh gi d liu cn i (t l phn lp gn ngang nhau) [30].

Precision ( chnh xc) trung bnh tt c m hnh. Trong bi ton ny, Precision tr li cho cu hi: Trong cc sa i c m hnh d on l "Sa i ph hoi", c bao nhiu sa i thc s l "Sa i ph hoi" [30]. Vi kt qu ny, nhn chung cn phi ci tin m hnh t Precision cao hn ng dng trong thc t.

Recall ( nhy) rt thp tt c m hnh. Trong bi ton ny, Recall tr li cho cu hi: Trong cc sa i thc s l "Sa i ph hoi", c bao nhiu sa i c m hnh d on trng [30]. Vi kt qu ny, nhn chung cc m hnh "tm sot" km cc "Sa i ph hoi", b st rt nhiu trng hp.

F1 rt thp tt c m hnh. F1 l trung bnh iu ha gia Precision v Recall [29]. Nhn chung, m hnh c F1 cao th c th xem l tt, nht l khi cn mt ch s nh gi khch quan trong trng hp Precision v Recall qu chnh lch [29].

Hnh 3. Precision & Recall [31]

Biện luận ứng dụng¶

Nhn chung, ngoi tr Accuracy cao nhng khng lin quan, th tt c nhng h s nh gi cn li u cho thy cc m hnh khng c kh quan p dng trong thc t. Tuy nhin, vn c tim nng ng dng nu nh c ci tin tt hn, theo 2 hng ng dng chnh.

  • Hng 1: S dng m hnh pht hin "Sa i ph hoi" trong cc chng trnh chng ph hoi t ng trn Wikipedia, nh ClueBot NG, li li nhng "Sa i ph hoi" mt cch t ng. Vi hng ny, vic pht hin chnh xc ln tm sot "Sa i ph hoi" u quan trng, nhng c l yu t pht hin chnh xc quan trng hn. V nu d on sai nhiu, li li nhm nhiu nhng sa i khng thuc din "Sa i ph hoi" th s gy kh chu cho ngi dng Wikipedia. Ging nh vic d on qu nhiu email quan trng thnh spam s gy kh chu cho ngi dng email. ng dng c hng ny, m hnh phi c Precision t cao n rt cao, v Recall th t trung bnh n cao; c th l Precision 85%, Recall 40%. Nh vy, trong cc m hnh hin ti, khng c m hnh no t c yu cu ny.

  • Hng 2: S dng m hnh trong cc chng trnh cnh bo nhng sa i c tim nng l "Sa i ph hoi", nhm hng s ch ca i ng tun tra vo nhm ny, thnh vin tun tra s ti nh gi v a ra quyt nh c li li hay khng. Vi hng ny, vic pht hin chnh xc ln tm sot "Sa i ph hoi" u quan trng, nhng c l yu t tm sot quan trng hn rt nhiu. V cng vic ti nh gi c con ngi x l sau , nhim v ca m hnh l phi tm sot, qut c nhiu nht nhng "Sa i ph hoi" thc s, tuy nhin cng khng nn chnh xc qu thp v s khin cng vic ti nh gi ca con ngi tr nn qu ph phm (do c qu nhiu sa i khng thuc din "Sa i ph hoi"). ng dng c hng ny, m hnh phi c Precision t trung bnh n cao, v Recall th t trung bnh n rt cao; c th l Precision 40%, Recall 40%. Nh vy, trong cc m hnh hin ti, khng c m hnh no t c yu cu ny. Nhng vn c th chn ly m hnh c Recall cao nht trong s , v hng ng dng ny kh an ton, khng gy nh hng n ton b ngi dng Wikipedia nh Hng 1 m ch gy p lc ln mt nhm nh thnh vin tun tra.

Nh vy, nu theo Hng 2, m hnh ca thut ton Gradient Boosting c th p ng c.

Phụ lục 3¶

L do trch chn 70 c trng n t nguyn tc loi b cc c trng c phng sai qu thp. S dng lp VarianceThreshold ca sklearn loi b cc c trng theo mt ngng phng sai cho trc, thy rng nu phng sai mc 0.5 th s loi c 25/90 c trng c phng sai di mc ny, cn li 65 c trng.

Tuy nhin, do 12/90 l bin nh tnh, do la chn con s trch chn c trng l 70 thay v 65. M x l c tham kho t How to Perform Data Cleaning for Machine Learning with Python (Machine Learning Mastery).

In [1]:
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from numpy import arange
from sklearn.feature_selection import VarianceThreshold

df = pd.read_csv('data/raw_revs.csv')
del df['rev_id']

X, y = df.iloc[:, :-1], df.iloc[:, -1]

thresholds = arange(0.0, 0.55, 0.05)
# apply transform with each threshold
results = list()

for t in thresholds:
    # define the transform
    transform = VarianceThreshold(threshold=t)
    # transform the input data
    X_sel = transform.fit_transform(X)
    # determine the number of input features
    n_features = X_sel.shape[1]
    print('>Threshold=%.2f, Features=%d' % (t, n_features))
    # store the result
    results.append(n_features)
    
# plot the threshold vs the number of selected features
plt.plot(thresholds, results)
plt.show()

Phụ lục 4¶

L do chn gi tr tham s C=80 ca SVM l khi thc hin kim tra tng quan gia C v F1 th C mc nh ca hm SVC (C=1.0) lm cho F1 rt thp v khng th pht hin c cc sa i ph hoi. Khi C tng th F1 cng thay i theo, v theo kt qu nhn c th C=80 s cho F1=0.137363 v C=600 s cho F1=0.182243.

Hnh 5. Tng quan C v F1

Tuy nhin, ch s Precision ca C=600 (Precision=0.351351) li khng kh quan bng C=80 (Precision=0.531915), v Recall gia 2 C cng khng qu chnh nh Precision. Do , quyt nh la chn tham s C=80 cho hm SVC xy dng m hnh.
